I heard a lot of good reviews from Verona locals.
My boyfriend and I decided to visit The Klassik for dinner.
Best decision of the week!
As soon as we walked in, we noticed the bar on the right side and the restaurant to the left.
Very clean and decorated with appealing modern decor.
We ordered the cheese curds as an appetizer, Doktor Burgers --- See uploaded photo, and the house made Snickers cheesecake.
All were delicious!
The service was wonderful and attentive.
Will definitely return.

